{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20171.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"id":200905,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Good job out there.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-2"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Here, have a cake from our shop."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Thank you, Mabayu."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Here, clear your Soul Gem with this."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-5"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Heh heh heh...@Thanks."},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"chara":[{"effect":"ef_adv_09","id":200905}],"se":"7210_souljem_01","textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-6"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200905}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Your foresight really is amazing."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Thanks to your abilities, I was able to find@the Witch quickly and take it down with ease..."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Just happy to be of help."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'm completely useless in battle@since I suck at using my scissors..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-10"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So how about I just stick to being@a strategist like this?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...Maybe? Haha."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Actually, you make a good point."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-13"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]An ace is most valuable when it's@kept hidden..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":250301,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Your power of foresight should only be@made known to trustworthy Magical Girls."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Uhh, wait..."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-17"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]There are other Magical Girls out there?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":250301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":250301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-19"},{"id":200905,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Even among Magical Girls,@there are many different types."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I personally believe in protecting people@from Witches..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-21"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But there are Magical Girls who don't@subscribe to that belief."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-22"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]There are those who only made@a contract to fulfill their wish..."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]As well as girls who are simply@satisfied with collecting Grief Seeds."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-24"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We're at odds with those types,@since we defeat Familiars."},{"chara":[{"id":250301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Because to them, that's like killing@the bird before it lays an egg."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-26"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Huh...@Is that how things work?"},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I can't imagine someone making@an enemy out of you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":250301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-28"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-29"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Either way, that works for me."},{"chara":[{"id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-30"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If I got targeted and held hostage,@I wouldn't have any means of fighting back."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200905,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-31"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So, I'll be the schemer in the shadows!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_013.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-32"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Let's go with the plan of keeping me@hidden away from sight!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":200905,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913005-002-33"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Heh heh heh..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
